# 🚀 COMPLETE BUSINESS WORKFLOWS
#
# 📚 End-to-end business scenarios with step-by-step instructions
#
# 💡 HOW TO USE:
# 1. Execute steps in sequence (A1, A2, A3, etc.)
# 2. Copy values from responses where indicated
# 3. Each workflow demonstrates a complete business flow
#
# 🔧 SETUP
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

###############################################################################
# 🛍️ WORKFLOW A: SUCCESSFUL E-COMMERCE ORDER
# Complete customer journey from browsing to purchase
###############################################################################

### A1. Check stock availability
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/stock/2d70d1dc-cd3a-4f40-afb0-52e16445bf36

### A2. Reserve stock for checkout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "2d70d1dc-cd3a-4f40-afb0-52e16445bf36",
  "quantity": 1,
  "request_id": "checkout-{{$timestamp}}-laptop",
  "timeout_seconds": 600,
  "reason": "Customer checkout - Laptop HP Pavilion 15"
}

### A3. Verify stock was reserved
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/stock/2d70d1dc-cd3a-4f40-afb0-52e16445bf36

### A4. Complete the purchase
# 📝 Copy reservation_id from A2 response
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/release
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservation_id": "PASTE_RESERVATION_ID_FROM_A2",
  "reason": "purchased",
  "request_id": "complete-{{$timestamp}}"
}

### A5. Final stock check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/stock/2d70d1dc-cd3a-4f40-afb0-52e16445bf36

###############################################################################
# 🛒 WORKFLOW B: ABANDONED SHOPPING CART
# Customer abandons cart, stock is automatically released
###############################################################################

### B1. Check initial stock
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/stock/47569eb2-fe19-43cb-929d-aedfd59dc199

### B2. Add to cart (reserve stock)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "47569eb2-fe19-43cb-929d-aedfd59dc199",
  "quantity": 1,
  "request_id": "cart-{{$timestamp}}-headphones",
  "timeout_seconds": 900,
  "reason": "Shopping cart hold"
}

### B3. Customer abandons cart
# 📝 Copy reservation_id from B2 response
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/release
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservation_id": "PASTE_RESERVATION_ID_FROM_B2",
  "reason": "cancelled",
  "request_id": "abandon-{{$timestamp}}"
}

### B4. Verify stock returned to available
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/stock/47569eb2-fe19-43cb-929d-aedfd59dc199

###############################################################################
# 📦 WORKFLOW C: WAREHOUSE RESTOCK
# Demonstrate inventory management operations
###############################################################################

### C1. Check current stock before shipment
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/stock/f7d85ff3-6dbf-4ee8-bd61-54453610e441

### C2. Receive new inventory shipment
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/stock
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_id": "f7d85ff3-6dbf-4ee8-bd61-54453610e441",
  "new_stock": 50,
  "adjustment_type": "restock",
  "reason": "Weekly SSD shipment received",
  "reference": "PO-{{$timestamp}}",
  "request_id": "restock-{{$timestamp}}"
}

### C3. Verify updated stock levels
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/inventory/stock/f7d85ff3-6dbf-4ee8-bd61-54453610e441

###############################################################################
# 💡 WORKFLOW TIPS
#
# A. E-commerce Success: Check → Reserve → Purchase → Complete
# B. Cart Abandonment: Reserve → Cancel → Release  
# C. Warehouse Ops: Check → Restock → Verify
#
# 🔄 Each workflow demonstrates:
# - Real-time stock visibility
# - Atomic operations (all succeed or fail)
# - Proper business logic handling
# - Audit trail with metadata
#
###############################################################################

###############################################################################
# 📦 WORKFLOW C: WAREHOUSE OPERATIONS
# Complete supply chain from receiving inventory to first sale
###############################################################################

### C1. Check current SSD inventory before shipment
GET {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/inventory/stock/f7d85ff3-6dbf-4ee8-bd61-54453610e441
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-ID: workflow-c-before

### C2. Warehouse receives new SSD shipment
PUT {{baseUrl}}{{apiVersion}}/inventory/stock
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-ID: workflow-c-receive

{
  "product_id": "f7d85ff3-6dbf-4ee8-bd61-54453610e441",
